245
00:17:20,448 --> 00:17:27,481
Oo, gusto ko 'yung batang lalaking may mahabang buhok.

246
00:17:27,504 --> 00:17:30,538
Ang gwapo niya, 'di ba?

247
00:17:30,561 --> 00:17:34,194
Malakas ba siya?

248
00:17:34,217 --> 00:17:40,057
Oo, pinakamalakas siya at mabait pa.

249
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:43,947
Nakakaintriga ang storya, ah.

250
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:50,070
Ito, every Friday night lang nag-a-ere.

251
00:17:50,093 --> 00:17:54,526
Sige, panoorin na lang ulit natin next week.

252
00:17:54,549 --> 00:17:58,095
Sige, gawin natin 'yon.

253
00:17:58,118 --> 00:18:02,356
Gusto mo, manood tayo habang kumakain ng mga meryenda?

254
00:18:02,379 --> 00:18:05,716
Ako na ang magdadala.

255
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,740
Scene 10: Usapang Pahinga at Part-Time Job

256
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:13,730
Alas-onse na pala ng gabi, ah.

257
00:18:13,753 --> 00:18:18,427
Oo, oras na para matulog.

258
00:18:18,451 --> 00:18:22,685
Bukas, anong oras ka gigising?

259
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:28,275
Bukas, day-off ko, kaya matutulog ako nang mahaba.

260
00:18:28,298 --> 00:18:31,238
Sige, okay naman.

261
00:18:31,261 --> 00:18:35,830
Ako, may part-time job pa rin bukas.

262
00:18:35,854 --> 00:18:37,891
Eh,

263
00:18:37,914 --> 00:18:41,687
Araw ng Linggo, may part-time ka pa rin?

264
00:18:41,711 --> 00:18:46,211
Oo, simula alas-nuwebe ng umaga.

265
00:18:46,234 --> 00:18:49,615
Ang hirap naman no'n.

266
00:18:49,639 --> 00:18:53,226
Anong oras ka matatapos?

267
00:18:53,249 --> 00:18:57,034
Alas-dos ng hapon matatapos ako.

268
00:18:57,058 --> 00:19:02,091
Ah, may oras ka pa sa hapon, ah.

269
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:08,181
Oo, sa hapon, lilinisin ko at maglalaba.

270
00:19:08,203 --> 00:19:12,637
Tutulungan kita sa paglilinis ng kwarto.

271
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:15,371
Talaga?

272
00:19:15,395 --> 00:19:18,153
Salamat.

273
00:19:18,176 --> 00:19:23,743
Eh, lagi ka namang nagluluto ng pagkain para sa akin.

274
00:19:23,766 --> 00:19:26,315
Salamat, malaking tulong 'yan.

275
00:19:26,338 --> 00:19:31,910
Sige, magkita na lang tayo bukas ng alas-tres para maglinis.

276
00:19:31,933 --> 00:19:34,666
Sige, intindido.

277
00:19:34,689 --> 00:19:39,356
Nakita mo na ba ang weather forecast ngayon?

278
00:19:39,379 --> 00:19:45,515
Oo, sabi maganda ang panahon bukas.

279
00:19:45,538 --> 00:19:49,679
Mabilis matutuyo ang mga labada, 'no?

280
00:19:49,703 --> 00:19:52,136
Oo nga, eh.

281
00:19:52,159 --> 00:19:55,992
Sasara na ang ilaw.

282
00:19:56,015 --> 00:19:59,954
Sige. Matulog ka nang mahimbing.

283
00:19:59,978 --> 00:20:02,617
Ingat, matulog ka nang mabuti.

284
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:05,340
Hanggang bukas.